107
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:18,319
Yang dari buku.

108
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:22,000
Maksud anda yang tradisional?

109
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,120
Jadi anda suka sekolah lama?

110
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:28,199
Adakah benar-benar ada perbezaan?

111
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,800
Ayuh, sekali lagi.

112
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,600
Okay.

113
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:01,360
- Berikan saya belon itu. - Sedikit lebih tinggi.

114
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,639
- Sedikit lagi ke kiri. - Jangan kacau.

115
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:04,519
Saya faham, tiada masalah.

116
00:09:04,519 --> 00:09:06,319
Itu lebih kurang betul.

117
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,266
Berhati-hati.

118
00:09:10,266 --> 00:09:11,960
masa berlalu.

119
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:14,520
Saya tidak percaya Krismas hampir tiba.

120
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:20,079
Saya masih ingat semasa saya kecil, ia adalah percutian kegemaran nenek saya.

121
00:09:43,940 --> 00:09:47,589
Tetapi sejak dia meninggal dunia,

122
00:09:47,589 --> 00:09:51,160
